      "content": "i understand but i've had a headache like this before and it always goes away with just one of these. i really cant get to a doctor today and the pain is making it hard to focus on my job. is there any way i could just take a smaller dose or maybe take it with some extra water to help protect my kidneys? i just need some relief right now.",
